      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四绿龙套同上，关羽上。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00002",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "正气冲霄汉，文光射斗牛。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00003",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "头戴金冠凤翅飘，凤眼蚕眉呈英豪。忠义扶定汉室主，上阵全凭偃月刀。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00004",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "某汉室关羽，与军师赌头争印，捉拿奸臣。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00005",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小校带马。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00006",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "背地里笑诸葛用兵不到，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00007",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "去大营他那里藐视吾曹。自幼儿读《春秋》韬略颇晓，为不平斩雄虎怒诛土豪。蒙圣母赐清泉改换容貌，走樊阳才结拜生死故交。初起手破黄巾立功不小，酒未冷斩英雄初试宝刀。过五关斩六将力保皇嫂，古城边斩蔡阳匹马单刀。将人马埋伏在华容小道，今日里一心要捉拿奸曹。",
      "text_length": 123
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00008",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "曹操到此，禀爷知道。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00009",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关羽下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00010",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "曹孟德在马上长吁短叹，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00011",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四青袍、曹八将、曹操同上。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00012",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "呵！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00013",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "手捶胸眼落泪苦怨长天。在中原领人马八十三万，实指望灭刘备踏翻江南。恨只恨诸葛亮诡计多端，黄公覆献连环火烧战船。只烧得众兵丁皮开肉绽，只剩下十八骑好不可怜。坐雕鞍勒丝疆用目观看，",
      "text_length": 88
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00014",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "笑",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "吓，哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00015",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "许褚"
      ],
      "text": "丞相发笑为哪般？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00016",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "笑是笑周郎见识浅，孔明袖内少机关。日出若有人和马，又恐失计难保还。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00017",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "龙套喊。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00018",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "一声未发人马喊，旌旗招展心胆寒。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00019",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "许褚看看，什么人的旗号？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00020",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
