      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "听说来了关美髯，不由孟德喜心间。走上前来把礼见，问声君侯驾可安。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00030",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小校"
      ],
      "text": "曹操到！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00031",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "耳边厢又听得人嘶马闹，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00032",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关羽上台子。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00033",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "纵蚕眉睁凤眼仔细观瞧：狭路上莫不是冤家来到，奉军令谁认你旧日故好。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00034",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "曹孟德在马上满面陪笑，尊一声汉君侯细听根苗：在赤壁中火攻败兵来到，望君侯开大恩放我回朝。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00035",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "三国中论奸雄算你曹操，一派的假殷勤袖里藏刀。俺今日用兵时何必发笑，奉军令捉拿你怎肯相饶。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00036",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "中了那小周郎苦肉计巧，只烧得众兵丁皮开肉焦。只剩下十八骑败兵来到，汉君侯若不信仔细观瞧。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00037",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "小校，查看曹操还有多少人马。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00038",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小校"
      ],
      "text": "你们站起了！一五，一十，十五，一、二、三！十八骑残兵败将！",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00039",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "军师吓，军师！你既能算，却不能料：慢说一十八骑残兵败将，就是一十八只猛虎，何足道哉！",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00040",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "料想他好一似鳌鱼吞钓，伤弓鸟纵插翅也难飞逃。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00041",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "说什么我好似鳌鱼吞钓，说什么伤弓鸟也难飞逃。想当初待君侯恩高义好，上马金下马银筵酒美姣。官封你寿亭侯爵禄不少，你本是大义人怎忘故交？",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00042",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "你虽然待我的恩高义好，我亦曾答报了你的功劳：斩颜良诛文丑立功报效，将印信悬高梁封金辞曹。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00043",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "我亦曾命人送文凭来到，临行时我又送美酒红袍。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00044",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "休提起送文凭令人可恼，诛孔秀，刺孟陶，王真被枭。过黄河斩秦琪文凭才到，谢丞相假人情哪在心梢！",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00045",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "在许昌曾许我云阳答报，为什么把人情一旦搬抛？",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00046",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "非是我忘却了云阳答报，因为你这奸曹罪恶难饶。在许田射鹿时把君欺藐，挟天子命诸侯势压群僚。逼死了董贵妃其罪非小，董贵妃，马腾病，欲扶汉朝。恨不得拿住了剥皮削草，上前来试一试偃月钢刀。",
      "text_length": 90
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00047",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "曹孟德在马上苦苦哀告，君侯吓！你何不留美名万古留标。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00048",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "往日杀人不展眼，铁打心肠软如棉。背地只把军师怨，左思右想难上难。关某岂做无义汉，宁斩我头挂高杆。小校摆开长蛇阵，忙开展，释放曹操回中原。",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00049",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "许褚看看什么阵势？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00050",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "许褚"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00051",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "许褚看。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00052",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "许褚"
      ],
      "text": "此乃是一字长蛇大阵。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00053",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "想是放你我逃走，走了罢。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00054",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "好个仁义关美髯，释放曹操回中原。苍天若睁三分眼，再与东吴怨报怨。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00055",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹操、曹八将、四青袍同下。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00056",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小校"
      ],
      "text": "曹操逃走！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00057",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "回营交令！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00058",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "悔当初错许他云阳答报，到今日顺人情又犯律条。叫小校你与爷辕门通报，",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00059",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关羽打马。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00060",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "就说是关二爷释放奸曹。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002013_e00061",
      "play_id": "01002013",
      "scene_id": "01002013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "同下。",
      "text_length": 3
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}